Subject: [PATCH] Upgrade to 2.191

---
 Dumper.pm     |  9 +++---
 Dumper.xs     | 26 +++++++++--------
 t/bugs.t      |  1 +
 t/deparse.t   | 15 +++++++---
 t/dumper.t    | 18 ++++++------
